window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>I've always heard there's a fine line between love and hate.</b></p> <p>No one told me that line could destroy me.</p> <p>Noah Fontaine. King of the school. My living nightmare. The object of my fantasies. My new stepbrother.</p> <p>I did whatever it took to survive him. Every day he took more of me. I just didn't expect him to take my heart.</p> <p>Because of the boy I once hated, I'd never be the same girl again.</p>"; 
